TECH_PARAM_1.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: statistics on Argos or GPS received data
TECH_PARAM_1.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: total number of Argos positions received.

TECH_PARAM_3.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: positioning (ARGOS message) - Class 1 - accuracy better than 1500m radius

TECH_PARAM_4.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: positioning (ARGOS message) - Class 2 - accuracy better than 500m radius

TECH_PARAM_5.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: positioning (ARGOS message) - Class 3 - accuracy better than 250m radius

TECH_PARAM_12.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: External bladder state at deployment (0: float stay at surface, 1: heavy float at deployment)
TECH_PARAM_12.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: External bladder state at deployment (0: float stay at surface, 1: heavy float at deployment)

TECH_PARAM_13.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Real valve opening time at surface
TECH_PARAM_13.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Duration of the basic valve actions.

TECH_PARAM_14.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: number of solenoid valve actions at the surface until the crossing of the GAP threshold

TECH_PARAM_15.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Grounding at Surface (0 : no grounding, 1 : grounding)
TECH_PARAM_15.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: is the float beached? - could be logical

TECH_PARAM_16.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Nb of valve actions in descent to Parking Depth
TECH_PARAM_16.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: number of valve actions between the crossing  of the gap threshold and the end of descent at park pressure

TECH_PARAM_17.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Nb of pump actions in descent to Parking Depth
TECH_PARAM_17.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: number of pump actions between the crossing  of the gap threshold and the end of descent at park pressure

TECH_PARAM_18.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Nb of entrance in Drift target range
TECH_PARAM_18.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: descent to park pressure: number of entries in margin around park pressure target - specifically, how many times the float enters the band of pressure surrounding the target park pressure (generally +/- 30db)

TECH_PARAM_19.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Nb of repositionning in Parking Stand-by
TECH_PARAM_19.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: number of times the float readjusts its buoyancy during park phase - using either the pump or EV

TECH_PARAM_20.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Number of valve actions during drift at Parking Depth
TECH_PARAM_20.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: number of valve actions during park phase

TECH_PARAM_21.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Number of pump actions during drift at Parking Depth
TECH_PARAM_21.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: number of pump actions while at park depth

TECH_PARAM_22.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Nb of valve actions in descent to Profile Depth
TECH_PARAM_22.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: number of valve actions during descent to start profile pressure

TECH_PARAM_23.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Nb of pump actions in descent to Profile Depth
TECH_PARAM_23.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: number of pump actions during descent to start profile pressure

TECH_PARAM_24.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: 1st Grounding day relative to cycle start
TECH_PARAM_24.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Day number when the float grounds for the first time (relative to mission start day).

TECH_PARAM_26.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Phase of the float life or cycle when the first grounding occurred.  See the manual for phase definition - this will vary with float type

TECH_PARAM_27.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: grounded flag , diagnostic bit - could also be logical?  Yes/no? 0/1? Or can be number of profiles during which the float grounded

TECH_PARAM_28.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Number of entrance in Profile target range
TECH_PARAM_28.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: descent to profile pressure: number of entries in margin around profile pressure target  - specifically, how many times the float enters the band of pressure surrounding the target profile pressure (generally +/- 30db)

TECH_PARAM_29.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Number of repositionning in Profile stand-by
TECH_PARAM_29.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: at profile pressure stand-by, number of times the float readjusts its buoyancy - using either the pump or EV

TECH_PARAM_30.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Number of valve actions during drift at Profile Depth
TECH_PARAM_30.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: number of valve actions while drifting at profile depth

TECH_PARAM_31.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Number of pump actions during drift at Profile Depth
TECH_PARAM_31.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of pump actions during drift at profile depth.

TECH_PARAM_32.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Number of pump actions in ascent
TECH_PARAM_32.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: number of pump actions between start and end of ascent

TECH_PARAM_33.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Number of pump actions in ascent for float lift-up
TECH_PARAM_33.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of pump actions needed to start the ascent.

TECH_PARAM_34.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Distinct frames emitted on descending profile

TECH_PARAM_35.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: statistics on Argos or Iridium received data
TECH_PARAM_35.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Provor frames received on descending profile

TECH_PARAM_36.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Distinct frames emitted on immersion profile

TECH_PARAM_37.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Distinct frames emitted on ascending profile

TECH_PARAM_38.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: statistics on Argos or Iridium received data

TECH_PARAM_39.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Number of descent slices in shallow zone
TECH_PARAM_39.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Descending profile reduction Number of slices in shallow zone - NTS

TECH_PARAM_40.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Number of descent slices in deep zone
TECH_PARAM_40.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Descending profile reduction Number of slices in deep zone - NTF

TECH_PARAM_41.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: total number of slices of the descending profile after reduction

TECH_PARAM_42.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: statistics on Argos or Iridium received data

TECH_PARAM_43.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Number of CTD measurements in drift

TECH_PARAM_44.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: statistics on Argos or Iridium received data
TECH_PARAM_44.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Distinct frames received with crc ok on immersion profile

TECH_PARAM_45.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: statistics on Argos or Iridium received data

TECH_PARAM_46.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Number of ascent slices in shallow zone
TECH_PARAM_46.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Ascending profile reduction Number of slices in shallow zone - NTS

TECH_PARAM_47.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Number of ascent slices in deep zone
TECH_PARAM_47.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Ascending profile reduction Number of slices in deep zone - NTF

TECH_PARAM_48.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: total number of slices of the ascending profile after reduction

TECH_PARAM_49.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: statistics on Argos or Iridium received data

TECH_PARAM_51.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Internal tube pressure [mbar] in profile depth

TECH_PARAM_52.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Battery voltage Drop at Pmax, Pump ON (With regards to Unom = 15.0 V, in dV)

TECH_PARAM_53.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: real time clock status - 1= OK, 0=not OK

TECH_PARAM_54.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: CTD Error (0 : no error, 1 Time-Out, 2, incomplete or broken frame, 3 = fast pressure default)
TECH_PARAM_54.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Flag indicating the status of the CTD (see manual) (could be reported as hex)

TECH_PARAM_55.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Phase of the float life or cycle when the CTD occurred.  See the manual for phase definition - this will vary with float type

TECH_PARAM_56.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Auto-test is performed at the beginning of the mission: Flag 0 = Problem, 1 = OK

TECH_PARAM_57.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Clock time of the last reset of the float

TECH_PARAM_58.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Clock time of the last reset of the float

TECH_PARAM_59.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of Emergency ascents - Internal count

TECH_PARAM_60.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of minutes elapsed in the day of the float first emergency ascent.

TECH_PARAM_61.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Pressure that triggered the first emergency ascent

TECH_PARAM_62.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Emergency ascent - pump actions at emergency depth

TECH_PARAM_63.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: 1st emergency ascent day relative to Cycle start
TECH_PARAM_63.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Day number of the float first emergency ascent (relative to mission start day).

TECH_PARAM_65.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Date of the beginning of buoyancy reduction (relative to mission start day).

TECH_PARAM_66.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Date of the beginning of buoyancy reduction (relative to mission start day).

TECH_PARAM_68.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: time when first stabilization appears during descent to park (tenths of an hour since midnight)

TECH_PARAM_69.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: time when park pressure is reached  (tenths of an hour since midnight)

TECH_PARAM_70.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: time when park pressure is reached

TECH_PARAM_71.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Descent to Profile Depth Start time
TECH_PARAM_71.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of minutes elapsed in the day at the beginning of the descent to profile depth.

TECH_PARAM_72.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Descent to Profile Depth Stop time

TECH_PARAM_74.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: time of the first transmission for this cycle

TECH_PARAM_81.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: time of the first transmission for this cycle

TECH_PARAM_82.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Number of repetitions for each argos message
TECH_PARAM_82.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of repeated transmissions of float data for each Argos message

TECH_PARAM_83.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of times technical message #1 has been received.

TECH_PARAM_84.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of times technical message #2 has been received.

TECH_PARAM_85.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of times parameter message has been received.

TECH_PARAM_86.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Time difference between first and last Argos float messages assigned to the cycle.
